===[[Pokémon Mezastar]]===
{{missing image|section|Artwork}}
Steven, in a version based on {{aniseries|PTS}}, appeared in [[Pokémon Mezastar]].<ref>https://pokemonmezastar.com/new/dc2.html</ref> In this game, Steven is seen using {{p|Cradily}}, a Shiny {{p|Metagross}}, {{p|Aerodactyl}}, and {{p|Aggron}}, with Aerodactyl being a Pokémon that he has not been seen using in ''Pokémon the Series'', although it could be a  [[List of cross-canon references|reference]] to [[Steven Stone|him]] using Aerodactyl in the [[core series]] games. In the [[Double Chain set 2 (Mezastar)|second Double Chain series set]], Steven also appeared as an opponent in an event that recreated the [[Masters Eight Tournament]] that ran from October 27 to November 21, 2022. Upon beating the character, the player can receive a Support Pokémon Ticket based on [[Steven's Metagross]], which can [[Mega Evolution|Mega Evolve]].<ref>https://pokemonmezastar.com/event/e2210142/</ref>

